The poor daughter of the Marquis, Teresse, who has been striving to save money day and night, was suddenly informed that she will be one of the &ldquo;Grand Duke's Consort Candidates.&rdquo;

&ldquo;Being a poor aristocrat such as myself, becoming a consort candidate is impossible for me&rdquo;&ndash; is how I should kindly refuse, but&hellip;

&ldquo;Every candidate will be granted 100,000 peir.&rdquo;
&ldquo;Possible employment as a court lady or lady attendant.&rdquo;

&quot;These generous conditions?!&quot;

&ldquo;I can be a court lady that I&rsquo;ve always longed for!&rdquo; Teresse thought. And with this in mind, she decided to head to the palace as a &ldquo;Consort Candidate.&rdquo;

However, what awaits her in the palace is a war with self-indulgent young ladies and other consort candidates! Will Teresse be appointed as a court lady or will she stand out from the rest as the Grand Duke's Consort?!

&bull; 1-2) &quot;I'm the Pet!&quot;
Shizuru is living alone with his mother who has difficulties paying the rent in time. In place of his mother, he goes to the landlord's house, Koushirou, to negociate the rent. Willing to do anything, he ends up being the substitute for Koushirou's loved dog, Catherine.

&bull; 3) &quot;Love Drive&quot;
Ogawa is always getting annoyed by Saeki who often yells at him. But does he really hate him or...?

&bull; 4) &quot;Manager is a Dangerous Job&quot;
Working as a manager for the top idol, Kamijyou Hikaru, isn't an easy job. But how far Nakatani is willing to go to supervise Hikaru?

&bull; 5) &quot;It's a Secret for Onii-chan&quot;
Spin-off about the younger brother, Touma, from &quot;Masaka Kore ga Koi Nante&quot; chapter 5.

&bull; 6) &quot;My Lover is My Bodyguard&quot;
A bodyguard and young master relationship.

&bull; 7) &quot;This is Surely Love&quot;
Sequel to &quot;Masaka Kore ga Koi Nante&quot;.

Shinonome Nagi, a college student who loves reading sensual novels in the newsports column, met with a writer he admires, the sensual novelist Shidou Tatsuo.

Shidou treats him like a child and swears that he could make him come with just a kiss &ndash; as it turns out, Shido's kiss technique was truly outstanding!

Since their first meeting, Nagi and Shidou got involved in intercrural sex, an encounter that inspired Shidou to produce a story which got him a new serialization!

&quot;Be my assistant and cooperate with me to produce the story, perverted brat.&quot;

&quot;Stop calling me a brat, old man!&quot;

&quot;Let's make this the most beautiful defeat ever!&quot;

Every year, the private high school Kido Academy's soccer club is just &quot;one step away.&quot; The fall of their second year, while starting up the new team, their coach suddenly gets pulled away by another school! And on top of that, the finishing blow for the greatly damaged club members, a new coach appears...!?

--Translation from the cover of volume 1

&quot;If you're going to study Medicine, then become a doctor who can look after me when I'm injured!&quot;

This is the promise that was made between Amamiya and his best friend Kaji soon before graduation. Flash forward a decade and Amamiya has become a skilled orthopaedist, while Kaji finds himself dealing with an injury that has brought his thriving football career to a premature end.

Hoping to cheer up his unemployed, recently-divorced friend, Amamiya takes Kaji out for dinner. Afterwards, a heavily-drunk Kaji gets into an accident that leaves him with no memory of the events following his high school years. In the heat of the moment Amamiya, who has long harbored unrequited feelings for Kaji, blurts out, &quot;I'm your lover. Please come home with me&quot;...!?

Final Fantasy XV Official Comic Anthology, &egrave; una serie manga ispirata al famoso videogioco della saga di Final Fantasy, basato sul XV capitolo&hellip; 
Il primo volume contiene 14 capitoli, di vita quotidiana dei personaggi, durante il loro viaggio; 
In collaborazione con higharollakockamamie, un inglese che traduce le tavole nella propria lingua &egrave; stato possibile tradurle in Italiano.
Le scan hanno l&rsquo;unico scopo di far conoscere quest&rsquo;opera, nella speranza che arrivi presto in Italia&hellip; bisogna sempre sostenere gli autori&hellip; ♡ 

Ps: all'interno trovate immagini colorate dalla sottoscritta

Katsura, a second year in his high school's archery club, has a hard time controlling his nerves. His &quot;secret weapon&quot; is his brother's best friend and childhood buddy, Sou! One hug from Sou and Katsura's nerves are soothed to a peaceful calm. But he can't keep Sou around him forever. As he wonders how he'll survive without Sou's hugs, his friend Kouichi suddenly asks if he can be the one to save him, and kisses him! What now?!

[b][u]Polish / Polski:[/u][/b]
[spoiler]Katsura należy do klubu łucznictwa. I wszystko byłoby wspaniale gdyby nie jeden problem &ndash; chroniczna niepewność przed oddaniem jakiegokolwiek strzału. Sekretną bronią w walce z nerwami jest najlepszy przyjaciel jego brata, a zarazem kolega z dzieciństwa &ndash; Sou&hellip; A raczej przytulanie przez Sou. Ale jak wiadomo, sytuacja musi się zmienić. Co z tego wyniknie? Zwłaszcza, że w pobliżu Katsury kręci się jego przyjaciel z klasy, Kouichi&hellip;
